(172, 97, 0, 11, 'Hero idea', 0, 77, 'Chaosy', 1383351114, 'Hello, as my first post I want to post an idea of mine. The hero is based on the necromancer class from an old game called "Dark age of Camelot".\r\n\r\n[img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110716133461/wowwiki/images/6/6b/BTNRaiseDead.png[/img] [size=xx-large][color=#1E90FF]Haunted Soul - INT[/color][/size]\r\n\r\nAbilites:\r\n\r\n[img]http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20090112020617/wowwiki/images/5/5c/BTNScourgeBuild.png[/img] [color=#FFD700]Split Soul - No Target[/color]\r\nThe Haunted Soul split apart his soul summoning a minion on the ground. The minion got [color=#FF0000]20%[/color] of the casters max hp and aslong as this minion is alive the caster is invurnable to  all damage. The minion got a very low movement speed and deals [color=#FF0000]10%[/color] of the caster int as damage. Max 1 minion summoned at the time. The minion must also be within a certain range else he will get teleported to the caster.\r\n\r\n[img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20090112040148/wowwiki/images/2/29/BTNRodOfNecromancy.png[/img]  [color=#FFD700]Haunt - Single Target[/color]\r\nThe Haunted Soul  puts a curse on the target. The debuff lasts for [color=#FF0000]6 seconds[/color] and this target takes [color=#FF0000]30%[/color] extra damage from the summoned minion. The target is also slowed for a low percentage.\r\n\r\n[img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20090513193314/wowwiki/images/7/72/PASBTNPlagueCloud.png[/img] [color=#FFD700]Harvest Life - Passive[/color]\r\nWhen the haunted soul kills an minions he permanently gains [color=#FF0000]1 hp[/color] and [color=#FF0000]1 stack of "stolen soul". You can have a maximum of [color=#FF0000]X stacks[/color].[/color]\r\n\r\n[img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20090112040221/wowwiki/images/c/ca/BTNSacrificialSkull.png[/img] [color=#FFD700]Unleash Souls  - No  Target[/color]\r\nThe Haunted Soul gains [color=#FF0000]10%[/color] maximum hp + [color=#FF0000]1%[/color] for each stack of "stolen soul" for [color=#FF0000]10 seconds[/color]. During this time your summoned minion will also deal the [color=#FF0000]ammout of stolen souls%[/color] extra damage When the effect expires he will stun nearby enemies for 1 seconds and lose [color=#FF0000]15%[/color] of his max hp. Useing this ability resets the "stolen souls buff.\r\n\r\n\r\nPlaysyle - I wanted a somewhat tanky character with a minion as the key ability. So you want to build up as many stacks of "stolen soul" as possible to prepare your Unleash Souls ability. You should consider yourself as a very tanky hero and basicly build hp together with some movement speed. Even if youre tank you should be able to put out acceptable damage on a single target.\r\nSo in short: play defensive early to stack up your buff and then once you have minion lvl 2 and the others  spells at lvl 1 try to burst a single target down to get some easy gold.\r\n\r\npros: very good survival, ok damage, extremely good if you let him farm up\r\ncons: low movement speed, weak early game, easly countered by slows and stuns.', '84.217.49.40', 1423520040, 1, 0, 77, 1383587772, 1, '', '', 0),
