(103, 67, 78, 11, 'RE: Hero Idea Bundles', 0, 0, 'S[ub]lime', 1335398470, 'Well I didnt really read your comments much.\n\n[quote]\nThe Drunken Brawler would be very difficult to balance due to the lack of Mana. (People probably would ask why he has an Intelligence score then and if he hasn''t, why he gains less Attributes per level than other heroes). And the Ultimate would collide with the other Panda in our Map, which is actually a Fire Panda.\n[/quote]\n\nOh why didnt I add mana? Ill update it.\nThe Drunken Brawler was intentionally made to collide with those fire heroes.\nYou may also call him a Support, but in a small way.\n\n[quote]\nCreating a Morphing Hero who has different skill sets clashes with the engine, both that of warcraft and our own triggers. And I''m not really in favor of the model. It looks good, but since Gen. Frank is merging animations, it moves funny.\n[/quote]\nI dont know how you say it clashes though.\nMaker made I fint Melee/Ranged attack switch system, which I got inspired from to make this hero.\nYes it moves funny though, especially the slashes. Might find a better one though or a better Anim Set.\n\nGonna update the two heroes. Tell me what you think :D', '113.103.135.51', 1902610227, 1, 0, 22, 1335398496, 1, '652b00163f06e73d918e552660785515', '', 0),
