(153, 85, 0, 65, 'HLW RoC - New Version ( v6.0 )', 0, 1, 'pred1980', 1338954798, 'Hey guys,\r\n\r\nSo two years after the release of 5.3b, I decided to start working on a new version, Hero Line Wars RoC v6.0. This is not a stable release, but rather a beta build. \r\n\r\nThis version comes with many small changes. Some of these changes include:\r\n\r\n- Some heroes have new, non-learnable, "innate" abilities.\r\n- New hero: Grugg the Thundermaul Ogre.\r\n- New hero: Shaz Kahal the Necromancer.\r\n- All-new terrain, eye-candy and look-and-feel. ^^\r\n- New games modes: All Intelligence (-ai), All Strength (-as) and All Agility (-aa) which limit hero choice.\r\n- Shrines now cost money instead of mana (this change may be reverted in the next version).\r\n- Balance changes with some auras, creeps and heroes.\r\n- New item: Magical Armor, which gives armour and intelligence and doubles as a mana potion.\r\n- Gargoyle Wings have been fixed and can effectively teleport you to your team''s circle. :D\r\n- Fixed "-switch" command for trading heroes at the beginning of a game.\r\n\r\nHowever, this map also has a few rather major bugs, most of which will be fixed with the 6.1 release, which is scheduled soon.\r\n\r\n[url=http://hlwroc.herobo.com/HLWRoCv6.0.w3m][b][color=#1E90FF][u]Download the Map[/u][/color][/b][/url]', '86.56.108.127', 1446538367, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'c5a633c8e81e5c83379c88610e60ac84', '', 0),
