(483, 'myfbconnect_fbsex', 'Sync sex', '<b>This option DOESN''T WORK PROPERLY at the moment.</b> Unfortunately, sex is one of the biggest problems I have to face off since it''s a custom profile field with values which vary from board to board. I''ll work on it. The synchronization works (but it causes fields to be italian, so if you are used to PHP you can modify its function in inc/plugins/myfbconnect.php). Just leave it disabled if you don''t want to use an useless button.', 'yesno', '0', 20, 58, 0),
